# Decision Integrity

- Always separate `Confirmed`, `Assumption`, `Risk`, `Deferred` and `Open Question` when discussing architecture or implementation direction.
- Never invent unsupported capabilities.
- Never present risky ideas as settled design.
- Never silently mix MVP scope with future scope.
- When uncertainty affects architecture or scope, document it instead of guessing.
